---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — Custos"
  description="Start a conversation about sovereign, POPIA-compliant AI for your SA medical aid, bank, or insurer. 25 minutes, no pitch."
>
  <section class="grid-bg">
    <div class="wrap-narrow" style="padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin: 0 0 1.5rem;"><span class="label-accent">Contact</span> &nbsp;//&nbsp; start here</p>
      <h1 class="h-display" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.75rem); max-width: 18ch;">
        25 minutes. No pitch.
      </h1>
      <p class="lead" style="margin: 1.75rem 0 0; max-width: 50ch;">
        If you are a CIO, CRO, or Head of Data at a SA medical aid, bank, or insurer, and you have been asked where your AI data lives without a clean answer, that is the conversation worth having.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="wrap-narrow" style="padding: 1rem 1.5rem;">
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap: 1.25rem;">
      <a href="mailto:hello@custosza.com?subject=Sovereign%20AI%20enquiry" class="card" style="display: block;">
        <p class="label" style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Email</p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 0.4rem; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fff;">hello@custosza.com &rarr;</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55;">The fastest way to reach Custos. Mention your industry and the AI workload you have in mind.</p>
      </a>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="label" style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">What happens next</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">A short call to map your AI workloads and where the regulatory exposure sits. If there is a fit, we scope a Readiness Assessment from there.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 2rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-subtle);">Cape Town, South Africa</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-subtle);">SAST · UTC+2</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
